cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper discusses the use of statistical topic models to summarize multiple sides of current events, which falls under the category of natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning algorithms (cs.LG) and the incorporation of multiple viewpoints (cs.IR). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of deep learning techniques (cs.AI) and the evaluation of the model's performance (cs.SI).
